ign: center; padding: 6px !important;\">\n	<a href=\"http://media.techz.vn/2012/11/07/watermarked-31352264688.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://media.techz.vn/2012/11/07/watermarked-31352264688.jpg\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline-table; max-width: 600px; height: auto; margin: auto !important;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 20px; text-align: center; padding: 6px !important;\">\n	<a href=\"http://media.techz.vn/2012/11/07/watermarked-41352264689.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://media.techz.vn/2012/11/07/watermarked-41352264689.jpg\" style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline-table; max-width: 600px; height: auto; margin: auto !important;\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 20px; padding: 6px !important; text-align: right;\">\n	Nguồn Internet</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 20px; padding: 6px !important;\">\n	Tags: <a href=\"http://didongviet.vn/tin-tuc/d/so-sanh-htc-one-va-htc-one-x+-tai-di-dong-viet\">So sanh HTC One X va HTC One X+</a></p>', '0', '', '<p>\n	0</p>\n', '0', '', '0', 'so-sanh-htc-one-x-va-htc-one-x.jpg', '1', '0', '0', null, 